Saturday:  It was a nice day. I think the best part is that I didnt work :-). I heard it was a madhouse there with lots of people argueing with the front desk and bitching. Im so mad I wasn't there >_>. Then I went to Sarah's lakehouse thingy. I think the highlight was the food. I had 2-3 hotdogs and some cooler ranch chips. Mmmmm. Oh Yeah. people where there that I knew, that was coo. We went swimming. I nearly got killed by chicks that wanted me and I then I got about 1000 mosquitoes all over my legs. but the highlight was the undercooked hotdogs lol :-) :-p

<_< and I wonder why people stop talking to me....

Sunday: I had to work today, 3-11pm. It was very boring but it was the first sunday that went by pretty fast. SWEET. my barber likes to drop by now since I told him I would let him slide and go swimming for free (you usually need a 400 buck membership or something to swim and use the fitness center for a year) but he told me I get free haircuts now so woo.. I like hooking people up now. so if you want to swim for free, ill allow it if you give me food or money...

School Update: My Official Stance is that I am having a semester off from WNEC to basically bring up grades, etc. I will be in the area for one semester and taking courses so I dont just sit around and do nothing.. wouldnt that be a shame. but it gives me plenty of time to work and make more money and hang out with all the plainfield people I know.. the 3 of em. I still plan to visit whenever I am just sitting around and I'm bored. One Semester will go fast :-)

More Boring News: I was bored last night (Saturday) since I have no life and no bottle of vodka with me. I decided to make the most badass collection CD eVAR!!. It is my "ULTIMATE weezer 4 disc collection". I just wanted to post that because I can. and I enjoy talking about the same topics over and over again and leaving out more interesting details of mah life...

Dare Reflection Time: I don't know what it has been lately, maybe its my "sexy new haircut" or something in the water. but I've been feeling a lot more spunk than usual :-) . I'm usually very mild mannered *hides giant <S> underneath my shirt* but I've been feeling motivated. and I don't know if alot of you know this but motivated darius is one BAD MOTHA FUCKA >_>             *motivation probably lasts one day*

Watch Out World. Especally If I end up buying Jimoneau's car.
I'll be mobile and causing trouble... HIDE YER DAUGHTERS <_<

Life Lately: Lets see, As I said. I got a haircut today. Its about time I was all hippyish! My barber asked where I worked and actually wanted to stop by and swim.. Usually you are only allowed if you got a membership, but If I'm on duty and you want to swim. Just drop by and I'll let you slide..... in exchange for sexual favors. So stop by sometime! but If you cause trouble. I get to call the cops. Work wasn't too bad today. I really wish we could swear or say sarcastic smartass remarks to people who complain and act retarded.

Complaining Guest: Oh Yeah? Well whats stopping me from getting my bags and going to Mohegan Sun and getting a room there??
My Brain: a.) go right the fuck ahead. b.) I doubt you would get a room when they are sold out, you douche
My Mouth: oh.. no.. please don't go, im sorry for the inconvinence... *forcably lowers rate 10 dollars* thank you for dealing with this, sir.

Other than that, I have been pretty good. I am enjoying this summer and really am thinking about planning some things and just overall changing my very relaxed and chill personality. I think Ill take some initiative and start actually caring about things most people do.. I think I'm growing up and maturing a bit... or maybe I just care a little bit more :-p

But I think I am going to either go to sleep so I can get some sleep so I might be able to see some friends tomorrow and maybe go out this week. I dont really work monday - thursday and I think I'll get a little bit more time to do something. maybe 6 flags or whatever. well catch ya later.....


P.S. btw, go here if you are a Harry Potter fan :-) http://snapeskau.ytmnd.com/

Rock that bitch baby. I think I wanna find time to either hang out or do something cool this week so I'll have to figure it out from there. My Life In General:  Hmm, I have been busy pretty much doing very minimal social activities. Went to NY for a weekend for a graduation... I hung out with Jessica and Jamie once a week or so ago before that... if you count that.. We drove around and shopped and they wanted me to bring my guitar so I can like.. play songs to them randomly as I walked around (...so they would get turned on).. bitches love the guitar.. :-) . Other than that, I have just been chilling around the house and town whenever I get a chance. My life is very calm

Summer Bummer: I'm taking one or two summer courses (Online classes are easy). So that should keep me busy by asking me to do about 2-3 useless assignments a week (>_>). Its not that bad and one of the classes requires me to creatively write here and there. I'm sort of getting good at creating poems/lyrics. but I'll get better at it as time continues. I think I would probably do this even if i wasnt take this course. Maybe I'll post some of my lyrics or songs (with guitar) in the future here for you all to "enjoy". (lol)

Online Companies:  I HAVEN'T gotten my super cool electric guitar pack yet.. Apparently its takes forever when you get free shipping.. They said on the thing.. It would take 7 days to get here.. okay thats cool... *after 7 days*.. I get an email from fedex.. saying the estimated date it would get here in another 6 days (I.E. today)... thats fine i guess... *comes today*. I learn that that was the time it would get to FEDEX... it will come in another 7 days.. Im pissed... If it doesnt come then.. Im going to kidnap their children.... >:o  >:o

*changes song to "Scotty doesnt know"*

SCOTTY DOESNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNT KNOOOOOW!!!!

 Work:  Today was the fourth of July Weekend. So naturally It was very busy (I sold us out though, woo woo). It was mostly calm but just progressive. But naturally that never stays that way on a saturday. Something has to happen involving intoxicated people.. Apparently we accidently checked in Heroin Cokeheads. So we had to pay extra watch to make sure nothing shady happened and all that.. It was very nice to deal with that...

Current Count of Stoned/Druggie People I ran into during work:  6+

 But Other than that, Work has been... Work.. but it =  Money Bay Bay!!
Well, That has been whats going on lately. I wish I had more interesting things to put but yeah.. I'm boring :-) ... SO BYE HONEYBUNCHES!! <3 <3

SUX IT!!!! *crotch chops*

Adult Swim -  It is so funny.. Its the most random adult dry humor ever.. its great.. I got back from work In a pretty crappy mood but then I put this on and it just made me laugh sooo much.. Robot Chicken had a bunch of claymation parodies/skits (with a twist) and other things..and other great shows such as ATHF, Space Ghost, 12oz mouse, Family Guy, Etc...  If I could define this humor as anything. I would describe it as "Stoner cartoons for stoners". It is just so stupid its awesome. with adult weird humor on the rise. I can forsee a super awesome solo channel.

Strongest Freak? lol - The next thing I changed to was this TLC  on the "Worlds Strongest Boy"... this kid's life must have sucked... the parents were like "NO TOYS AND NO FRIENDS. just make money for me". This kid just works out and poses for perverts on the internet... >_>. I mean cmon.. He can do a RVD split weightlifting (where you do a split on chairs and hold weights) at just 9 years old.. who the fuck does that at 9... WHAT A FUCKING FREEK!...

Green Day Diss - There was this article where Green Day met their Punk Idol, and he totally dissed them and said that he didnt know who they were and they were "not punk".. now let me tell you.. that has to suck...  you can read about it here .

Friends/Work - I haven't done much.. I was mostly working, practicing chords, I hung out with some friends during the weekand.. It was pretty enjoyable I look forward to having more opportunities to hang out and see people. Word... now back to:

Well I'm going to go since I'm tired and this is just me typing out very random sleepy thoughts.. Yep.. I'm going to sleep then I'm going to wake up and either swim somewhere or sleep listening to Weezer. Peace out nugs! Darius
